episodes.title: Genesis Talks About Online Bullying From YouTubers, Nature Boy Cult Members, & More | Talk2Me Ep.2
episodes.description:
Yes, we changed the spelling of the title. "Talk 2 Me Podcast" is on episode 2. Today's show features DJ Genesis who talks to us about her life growing up in New Jersey, music career, and online bullying. Genesis & I have been through a lot on this platform. 

It was nice to get to know Genesis on a deeper level. Please subscribe to this channel for more. Also follow DJ Genesis: https://www.youtube.com/@Djgenesisdetroit
